{"tid":1665574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有冇人諗過］點解之前警察醫院打人拎到cctv?!!831又唔得","createTime":"2019-10-20T15:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:48:31.000Z","uid":180670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"486dc108fce8728d6e2333a55d7e99957f14f0ba","tid":1665574,"uid":180670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"上次民主派夾住事主就可以拎到CCTV 片段，噤係咪同一方法可以要求黨鐵交出831 片段？<br />\n<br />\n彥琳雖然離開左，但事發當日，噤多人經過hkdi / hktvmall/ 地鐵附近，呢啲市民可唔可以做事主要求交出相關時段cctv ?? 有冇人諗過可唔可行？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//北區醫院接獲議員轉介該病人索取於「紊亂病人休息室」留醫期間閉路電視影像複本的申請後，按個人資料（私隱）條例及醫管局相關實務守則規定處理，並向申請人提供有關資料。<br />\n<br />\n院方曾詢問該病人是否需要報警處理，對方表示並無需要；病人留院期間，亦無向醫護人員及院方提出投訴。北區醫院表示，會配合警方有關調查工作。 //<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7%E8%99%90%E6%89%93%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5-%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%93%E5%BB%B7-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%BD%E8%A1%8C%E9%85%B7%E5%88%91%E5%8F%AF%E5%9B%9A%E7%B5%82%E8%BA%AB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25BB%25B7-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%2585%25B7%25E5%2588%2591%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%259B%259A%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%25BA%25AB%2F&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtjZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=771f1214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%2599%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5-%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%258D%2593%25E5%25BB%25B7-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25BD%25E8%25A1%258C%25E9%2585%25B